P1. ∀x, (A x = B x)

A1. ∀A, ∀B, (A = B) = ∀x, ((A x) = (B x))

1. (A = B) = ∀x, ((A x) = (B x))               [A1, by specialization]
2. A = B                                       [1, P1]
3. (fuse A C) = (fuse A C)                     [by eq_refl]
4. (fuse A C) = (fuse B C)                     [2, 3, by subst]
5. ∀A, ∀B, ((fuse A C) = (fuse B C)) = ∀x, ((A x)(C x) = (B x)(C x))  [A1, by specialization]
4. ∀x, ((A x)(B x) = (B x)(C x))               [4, 5, by subst]